{"tid":1267771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[G20] 支那又遲到 巴西總統取消與習總會面","createTime":"2019-06-30T05:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T08:03:08.000Z","uid":3822,"like":314,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc0141cc2ef26ec132cd6bf6e17f0d08874487c","tid":1267771,"uid":3822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QCYDQDe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQCYDQDe.png&h=1880701a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在日本大阪舉行的G20峯會，昨日焦點是中國國家主席習近平與美國總統特朗普舉行會談，但原來習近平昨日也約定與巴西總統博爾索納羅（Jair Bolsonaro）會面，可是習總與中國代表團卻沒有依時出現，博爾索納羅在等候25分鐘後，決定取消與習總的會面。<br />\n<br />\n彭博社的報道指出，博爾索納羅原定在當地時間昨日下午2時半與習近平舉行雙邊會談，可是習總與中方官員一直沒有出現，至下午2時55分，巴西政府發言人向在場的記者宣佈這場會面已經取消，更直言：「這場會議已經耽延太久，我方在雙邊會談室空等。」巴西代表團隨即返回酒店收拾行李，準時坐飛機回國。<br />\n<br />\n習近平與特朗普會面後參與哪些行程，內地媒體沒有報道，中央電視台則在昨日傍晚6時已經報道，習近平與出席G20的中國代表團已經返抵北京，一般而言，從大阪飛往北京的航程約為2小時40分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n這是中國代表團在G20峯會上，第二次出現集體遲到，習近平日前與日本首相安倍晉三會面時，被記者拍到中方代表團卻齊齊遲到，習近平一人獨坐會議枱的一邊，面對安倍及其他日本官員，場面相當尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n彭博社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190630/59772374?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F59772374%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGlSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=a39aae10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F59772374%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=33e65639\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190630/59772374?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"d5453845619228d00d1ad71ffb62b1e0efaed371","tid":1267771,"uid":29219,"like":124,"dislike":1,"score":123,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:13:46.000Z","msg":"好大既官威.jpg"},{"pid":"7bfa417b5e4ce98583b94f8a1679993076a814e3","tid":1267771,"uid":3122,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:14:15.000Z","msg":"成撚日遲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6888efdd0163810b610238acbe00c8e4fccddc9d","tid":1267771,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"quote":{"pid":"7bfa417b5e4ce98583b94f8a1679993076a814e3","tid":1267771,"uid":3122,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:14:15.000Z","msg":"成撚日遲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:15:39.000Z","msg":"有到算係咁"},{"pid":"5a06a0587a4fe03607fc28cd3b8ae76859b88a05","tid":1267771,"uid":3822,"like":136,"dislike":0,"score":136,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:18:08.000Z","msg":"習種：你班撚樣上次掉低我一個on99，今次我都唔嚟了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164fa023439475b2e44f702d1b542404421697f9","tid":1267771,"uid":78122,"like":124,"dislike":0,"score":124,"quote":{"pid":"6888efdd0163810b610238acbe00c8e4fccddc9d","tid":1267771,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"quote":{"pid":"7bfa417b5e4ce98583b94f8a1679993076a814e3","tid":1267771,"uid":3122,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:14:15.000Z","msg":"成撚日遲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:15:39.000Z","msg":"有到算係咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:18:25.000Z","msg":"可是習總與中方官員一直沒有出現<br />\n標題寫遲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係缺席呀"},{"pid":"385f94afa340a92cab420dce5753be8cd3bd76b1","tid":1267771,"uid":69746,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:18:59.000Z","msg